			<div class="content" id="post-content-1699020">
									

<p>Yes, that was a somewhat humorous note at the end, but it's also one that can &amp; does happen. I've worked at enough places that used form letters where, yes, you hit the wrong key or just accidentally forget to hit a key at all, and the letters go out to print. And usually, they get picked up, put in envelopes, and mailed by office assistants who don't even look at the contents because they don't have time to and it's not their job anyway.</p>

